      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. \ud83d\ude97 It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like an absolute dream and looks stunning from every angle. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
