    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector: a pristine E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is superlative, with a documented reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is a concours-level example with flawless paint depth and a tight, responsive steering rack, representing the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics.",
      "price": 49200.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
