    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s masterpiece, preserved in climate-controlled storage and maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep-gloss finish with a professional ceramic coating, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather is supple and matte, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that signature factory-fresh scent. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the tactile switchgear, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, chronological service history performed exclusively by master technicians. With an immaculate undercarriage and low mileage, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in peak condition. It is, quite simply, indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
